    dc:description "FIGURE 2 A–F. Gongylonema beveridgei Mawson, 1971. A, Cephalic end female paratype, en face view. B, Anterior end, female paratype, lateral view. C, Vulva and vagina paratype female, ventral view. D, Posterior end holotype male, ventral view. E, Posterior end female allotype, lateral view. F, Right spicule and gubernaculum holotype male, lateral view. Scale bars: Figs. 2A, 2B, 2D= 20 µm, Figs. 2C, 2F = 50 µm. Fig. 2E = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7624107/files/figure.png" ;
